# Test your FastAPI endpoints

### Register new user
POST http://localhost:8000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Login and get JWT token
POST http://localhost:8000/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=dilshan&password=123

###

### Get current user profile (replace TOKEN_HERE)
GET http://localhost:8000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJkaWxzaGFuIiwiZXhwIjoxNzcyMjI3ODk2fQ.Zcz9Oz4W1_VYKENJ7aP0d2XVIwerMY4y5GHrvkl16Jg